<!-- Our Story Section -->
<section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                <div class="text-center mb-5">
                    <h2 class="section-title">The Baklovah Journey</h2>
                    <p class="section-subtitle">From a family recipe to a beloved restaurant</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="mb-5">
                    <p>Baklovah Restaurant was born from a passion for authentic Middle Eastern cuisine and a desire to share our cultural heritage with our community. Our journey began in 2010 when our founder, Ahmed Hassan, decided to transform his family's generations-old recipes into a dining experience that would bring people together.</p>
                    
                    <p>What started as a small family-owned cafe has grown into a beloved restaurant known for its warm hospitality, vibrant atmosphere, and most importantly, delicious food that honors traditional recipes while embracing modern culinary techniques.</p>
                    
                    <p>The name "Baklovah" pays homage to one of the most iconic Middle Eastern desserts, symbolizing the sweet connection between our cultural roots and the joy we aim to bring to our customers through food.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="text-center mb-5">
                    <img src="/images/customer/restaurant-story.jpg" alt="Baklovah Restaurant Story" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Our Values Section -->
<section class="py-5 bg-light">
