                        <h4 class="card-title">Authentic Cuisine</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">We are committed to preserving the authenticity of traditional Middle Eastern recipes while adding our own creative touch. We use only the freshest ingredients and time-honored cooking techniques to create dishes that transport you to the heart of the Middle East.</p>
