                        <h4 class="card-title">Family & Community</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">We believe in the power of food to bring people together. Our restaurant is designed to be a welcoming space where families and friends can gather, share meals, and create lasting memories. We're not just serving customers; we're building a community.</p>
