                        <h4 class="card-title">Sustainability</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">We are committed to operating our restaurant in an environmentally responsible way. From sourcing local ingredients whenever possible to minimizing food waste and using eco-friendly packaging for takeout orders, we strive to reduce our environmental footprint.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
